@startuml sd_TaxService_calculateTax
skinparam backgroundColor #F9FAFB
title TaxService.calculateTax(…) - 个税累计预扣法计算

actor "调用方" as Client
participant "SalaryCalculationService" as CalcSvc
participant "TaxService" as TaxSvc
participant "TaxConfigRepository" as TaxRepo
participant "TaxConfig\n(实体)" as TaxConfig

Client -> CalcSvc: calculateAll(yearMonth, trialRun, username)
CalcSvc -> TaxSvc: calculateTax(yearMonth, monthlyIncome,\ncumulativeIncome, cumulativeExempt,\ncumulativeDeduction, cumulativeTaxPaid,\nspecialDeduction)
note right of TaxSvc #F0F8FF
  **计算过程:**
  1. year = 2024, month = 03
  2. 减除费用 = 5000 × 3 = 15000
  3. 应纳税所得额 = cumulativeIncome
     - cumulativeExempt - 15000
     - cumulativeDeduction
     - specialDeduction
  4. if ≤ 0 → return 0
end note
TaxSvc -> TaxRepo: findByYearAndActiveTrueOrderByLevel(year)
TaxRepo --> TaxSvc: List<TaxConfig>\n(7级税率表)
note right of TaxSvc #F0F8FF
  **按级距计算:**
  等级1: 0~36000 × 3%
  等级2: 36000~144000 × 10%
  等级3: 144000~300000 × 20%
  ...
  累计税额 = Σ(每级金额×税率)
  本月应缴 = max(0, 累计税额 - 已缴)
end note
alt 无配置
  TaxSvc -> TaxSvc: getDefaultBrackets()\n使用默认7级税率
end
TaxSvc --> CalcSvc: double (本月应缴个税)
CalcSvc --> Client: 保存到SalaryRecord
@enduml
